parameters: The explorer is taking a break...

Phew... The enemies and the protection of the ruins are becoming
troublesome.

Well, \c[6]it's not like going deeper is mandatory.\c[0] It's wise to
withdraw once you're satisfied with a certain amount of profit. After
all, our lives are at stake.
Oh, hello. I'm glad you're not a grave robber.

I'm more interested in investigating as historical sites than
treasures, so feel free to take any nearby treasure chests.
